tika.dc.description:
For fans of New York Times bestselling authors E. L. James, Sylvia Day, and J. Kenner comes the first part of international bestselling author Marina Anderson's erotic series The Dining Club.

Part One: Desire

With an insatiable appetite for all things naughty, Grace thought she and her gorgeous financier boyfriend, David, had experienced more than their share of sensual adventures. But when David invites her to join him at the Dining Club, a hidden, secret society where members can explore all their darkest desires, Grace embarks on the sexual journey of a lifetime . . .

David introduces Grace into a world she'd never imagined existed-one full of erotic challenges. If she passes the tests, she is promised ecstasy beyond her wildest fantasies. If she fails, she's forbidden to ever set foot in the exclusive club again. But even as David's seductive commands make Grace feel more daring than ever before, she begins to fear...
